title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland Auditorium Arena on 1981-12-26
lineage: Master Cassettes (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.6 MHz)> dBpoweramp 2496 > Adobe Audition 3.01 > TLH flac2496
taper: Joani Walker patched out of Jim Voss
description:
Set I
Alabama Getaway-> Promised Land, Candyman-> Little Red Rooster, Big Boss Man, Me & My Uncle-> Big River, Bird Song, It's All Over Now, Big Railroad Blues, Let It Grow
Set II
Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain-> Estimated Prophet-> He's Gone-> Drums-> The Eleven Jam-> Truckin'-> Black Peter-> Around & Around-> One More Saturday Night, E: Don't Ease Me In
